/a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">946d</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:947e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">947e</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῆς εὐθύνης ἀπολύειν τινά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:571\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">571</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰς εὐ. τὰς τοῦ βίου</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the accounts rendered</tr_> of your life, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0402.tlg001:262:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Alex.\">Alex.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">262.8</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0018.tlg001:2:214\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.214</biblScope></bibl>, al. (On the accent see Hdn.Gr.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0018.tlg001:1:257:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.257.37</biblScope> </bibl>: the later form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐθύνη</foreign>, nom. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐθὺναι</foreign> is sts. found in codd. of early writers, as <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg010.perseus-grc1:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.27</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:326e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\">